      "textAlign": "left",
      "text": "struct Stack<T> {\n    items: Vec<T>,\n}\n\nimpl<T> Stack<T> {\n    fn push(&mut self, item: T) { self.items.push(item); }\n    fn pop(&mut self) -> Option<T> { self.items.pop() }\n    fn peek(&self) -> Option<&T> { self.items.last() }\n}",
